channel.title: 99 Cooking Party - [DONE] 99 Cooking Achieved!
channel.description:
[center][size=24pt]Account name: Davidi2[/size][/center]
Well I'm 8k fish away from 99 cooking, and I plan to get there tonight! So I'm having a party, anyone can come. Here's the schedule:
Start - F2P world (TBA #), Varrock Square, I light a fire and cook my last fish for 99 cooking. You can say 'gratz' or 'fk you david' or whatever, and then we walk to the Cooking Guild. Then me and those of us who are members will world hop to a member world (TBA #) and I go in and get my cape. You say 'gratz' or 'fk you david' or whatever, and then we hop back to the FTP world and do stuff.
More info: Time - 1 AM PST(GMT -8) (4:00 am EST, 9:00 AM GMT) Worlds - TBA
To get the world #'s, enter my Clan Chat.
[b]I will have Private Chat OFF[/b]. Enter my CC (I will be on approximately 2 hours before the event) for world numbers and other information.
I understand it's a weird time, and a lot of you wont make it, but that's ok, I don't expect anyone to stay up that late.
[b]If you [u]plan on coming[/u] please fill this out:[/b] (and only if you are coming!) Account name: Combat level: P2P or FTP: Timezone:
If you have any 99's please bring the capes!
